28:55.330 --> 28:59.027
- If only every problem could be
solved with a simple waltz.

29:04.410 --> 29:07.868
Jack's treating you
like a suspect.

29:07.910 --> 29:11.038
Pointing fingers
in the dark.

29:13.980 --> 29:15.948
- I've walked away
from Will,

29:15.980 --> 29:18.744
