his accusations.

29:20.550 --> 29:23.451
- I've walked away too.

29:23.490 --> 29:25.958
I can't forgive Will
for what he did to you.

29:28.260 --> 29:30.967
I just want to walk away
from all of it.

29:31.000 --> 29:34.128
- What does walking away
leave us?

29:34.170 --> 29:36.161
- Each other.

31:49.000 --> 31:50.536
- Hello, Dr. Gideon.

